<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.4">
<l>kaṇṇil maṇalkoṭu tūvik kāliṉāl pāyntaṉai yeṉṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>eṇṇarum piḷḷaikaḷ vantiṭ ṭivarāl muṟaippaṭu kiṉṟār</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉē veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāy kaṇṭārō ṭētīmai ceyvāy</l>
<l>vaṇṇamē vēlai yatoppāy vaḷḷalē kāppiṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ! Countless children come to complain,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying again and again that you pounce with [your] feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">thrashing about and scattering sand in [their] eyes.</l>
<l>You who does mischief with [all] who see [you]!</l>
<l>You who stands in Veḷḷaṟai! Liberal One!</l>
<l rend="indent">You who resembles the colour of the sea,</l>
<l>Come so that [I can] fasten a Kāppu!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
